commands.name: az synapse managed-private-endpoints create
commands.summary: Create a synapse managed private endpoints.
examples:
az synapse managed-private-endpoints create --workspace-name testsynapseworkspace \
  --pe-name testendpointname \
  --file @path/test.json
test.json {"privateLinkResourceId": "/subscriptions/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/resourceGroups/test/providers/Microsoft.Storage/storageAccounts/test", "groupId": "blob"}

commands.name: az synapse managed-private-endpoints delete
commands.summary: Delete synapse managed private endpoints in a workspace.
examples:
az synapse managed-private-endpoints delete --workspace-name testsynapseworkspace \
  --pe-name testendpointname

commands.name: az synapse managed-private-endpoints list
commands.summary: List synapse managed private endpoints in a workspace.

commands.name: az synapse managed-private-endpoints show
commands.summary: Get a synapse managed private endpoints.
examples:
az synapse managed-private-endpoints show --workspace-name testsynapseworkspace \
  --pe-name testendpointname
